{"tid":2489222,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"三十秒科學–癌症所導致的體重流失(4)","createTime":"2021-04-14T21:13:24.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-15T13:33:00.000Z","uid":38861,"like":19,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c940f86030dd43dc7ff93230c4a2220c74e96262","tid":2489222,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T21:13:25.000Z","msg":"要理解為何癌症會導致肌肉萎縮，其中的一道辦法就是對比萎縮肌肉與正常肌肉有甚麼分別，再以推敲其相關的機制。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zhV5oyE.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzhV5oyE.png&h=d3612263&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖2)研究發現，患癌老鼠的萎縮肌肉中，其名為ZIP14的蛋白質含量特別高企，且在患癌的老鼠但其肌肉並沒有萎縮的情況下， ZIP14的蛋白質含量並沒有顯著提升。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7apRi61.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7apRi61.png&h=087b7179&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n(圖3)ZIP14蛋白質的主要作用是把鋅 (Zinc)輸送到細胞裡頭。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sRSvzFp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsRSvzFp.png&h=6a3a4662&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n科學家量度因癌症而導致萎縮的肌肉，發現肌肉的鋅 (Zinc)含量的確是比正常肌肉的為多，與其ZIP14蛋白質含量不謀而合。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n(圖4)利用基因工程移除ZIP14蛋白質的話，可以見得到患癌老鼠的肌肉細胞橫切面並沒有顯著的減少。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7HyR3yN.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7HyR3yN.png&h=7b54539e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再作一系列的實驗後，科學家推斷當癌細胞所釋出的TGFa/b物質到達肌肉位置後，便會引起肌肉ZIP14蛋白質含量上升，因而引起肌肉萎縮。<br />\n<br />\n科學家們現正研究如何針對ZIP14蛋白質來抑制癌症所引致的肌肉萎縮，結果適目而待。<br />\n<br />\n如果想我快啲出文的話，請入去Penana網站科普專欄&ndash;薯不揀單俾一個like以及Bookmark，這對我非常之重要。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fstory%2F66244%2F%25E7%25A7%2591%25E6%2599%25AE%25E5%25B0%2588%25E6%25AC%2584-%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%258F%2580%25E5%2596%25AE%2Ftoc&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=cab441c5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/story/66244/%E7%A7%91%E6%99%AE%E5%B0%88%E6%AC%84-%E8%96%AF%E4%B8%8D%E6%8F%80%E5%96%AE/toc</a><br />\n<br />\n同時亦可以在Penana網站裡按「買一嚿/半嚿薯仔」，以課金的方式推動我繼續搜羅資料寫文，多謝。<br />\n<br />\nLink:<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.penana.com%2Fuser%2F27349%2F%25E8%2596%25AF%25E4%25BB%2594%25E8%2581%259E%25E8%258C%25B1%25E8%258E%2589%2Fportfolio&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=8eb000bc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.penana.com/user/27349/%E8%96%AF%E4%BB%94%E8%81%9E%E8%8C%B1%E8%8E%89/portfolio</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非Facebook及IG重開侵侵的account，否則我的IG將不會再作更新，只會寄居本土LIHKG及Penana。<br />\n <br />\nRef1:<a href=\"https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29875463/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2F29875463%2F&d=RjdfG9uxtkM%2FelS3aO62sFuXAffr%2FfAYLX%2F1af%2FGhNY%3D&h=5c665387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://pubmed.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/29875463/</a>"},{"pid":"f4c69195b8733e2ecc49196e73d449d1c350b2d7","tid":2489222,"uid":246336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T21:20:40.000Z","msg":"啲鋅係咪都有份令肌肉萎縮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d24b7676748134ae2d31be877e075127ec9aeae7","tid":2489222,"uid":38861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f4c69195b8733e2ecc49196e73d449d1c350b2d7","tid":2489222,"uid":246336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T21:20:40.000Z","msg":"啲鋅係咪都有份令肌肉萎縮？<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/scratching.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-04-14T21:21:07.000Z","msg":"應該就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3e061f1e40f6c1095f5d1dd7baab00f753ec9f9f","tid":2489222,"uid":240004,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy"